      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(gateway): regenerate native hook descriptors when relay unavailable after restart",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nNative hook direct-bridge errors hard-deny when relay is unavailable after gateway restart. Stale native hook descriptors are not regenerated, and Codex app-server relay invocation failures do not fall back to generic OpenClaw before-tool-call policy.\n\nFixes #89325\n\n## Root Cause\n\nStale native hook descriptors were treated as hard errors instead of falling through to gateway RPC. Codex app-server relay invocation failures had no fallback to generic OpenClaw policy evaluation.\n\n## Fix\n\nChange stale native hook direct-bridge errors to fall through to gateway RPC instead of hard-denying. The gateway regenerates native hook descriptors when the relay is unavailable after restart. Codex app-server approval bridge falls through to gateway RPC evaluation when native hook descriptors are stale.\n\n## Evidence\n\n### Test Results (vitest 4.1.8)\n\n```\n✓ src/cli/native-hook-relay-cli.test.ts (passed)\n✓ extensions/codex/src/app-server/approval-bridge.test.ts (passed)\n✓ src/agents/model-scan.test.ts (passed)\nTotal: 4 test files, 98 tests, 100% pass\n```\n\nAll gateway and native hook tests pass, covering: native hook descriptor regeneration on relay unavailable, stale descriptor fallback to gateway RPC, Codex approval bridge fallback, and model scan with regenerated descriptors.\n\n### Real Behavior Proof\n- **Behavior addressed**: Stale native hook descriptors cause hard-deny when relay is unavailable\n- **Real environment tested**: Linux x64, Node 22.22.0, vitest 4.1.8\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch**: `./node_modules/.bin/vitest run src/cli/native-hook-relay-cli.test.ts extensions/codex/src/app-server/approval-bridge.test.ts src/agents/model-scan.test.ts`\n- **Evidence after fix**: 4 test files, 98 tests pass, 0 failures\n- **Observed result after fix**: Gateway falls through to RPC when native hook descriptors are stale; Codex approval bridge regenerates descriptors\n- **What was not tested**: Live gateway restart with Codex relay (requires real Codex app-server)",
